                    <td>Recently I noticed something peculiar. I lose mana upon zoning. From 100% mana I go down to 97% mana.

I noticed that this is exactly the amount of mana that I also lose when I remove my intricate wooden figurine (pop charm, with some pop flag stats and ldon adventure stone stats) and place it back in my inventory. I wonder if this is related.

I /bug reported it, so hopefully they will find out what is wrong.

Any other bards who have noticed something similar happen? With me it happens ...</td>
